  "prompt": "What is the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, salaries can vary based on experience, skills, company size, and market demand. Generally, the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai typically ranges from AED 14,000 to AED 30,000 per month. Entry-level positions might start around AED 10,000, while highly experienced consultants can earn significantly more, sometimes exceeding AED 40,000 per month.\n\nFor precise and up-to-date information, it's always best to refer to local salary surveys, job postings, and industry reports, or consult with recruitment agencies that specialize in the IT sector in Dubai.",
